== About

Simple and clean calculator, wich is written on Jquery.

Just link these 2 files to your directory.

== For Ruby-on-Rails

Place these 2 files in your assets folders
* assets/javascripts
* assets/styles

Make sure, that you have jquery-rails gem

== For others

Link these files in your HEAD-tag

* <script src="/assets/calculator.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
* <link href="/assets/calculator.css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />

Make sure, that you already downloaded and linked Jquery or Jquery-min to your site.

Good luck :)
